snippet.title: Dune: Spice Wars - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Control the spice, control the universe.

Vie for total domination of the spice in Dune: Spice Wars, an upcoming 4X RTS game set in the DUNE universe. What House will you lead to victory?

Coming to early access 2022.

Wishlist on Steam: https://bit.ly/3rFTkLS
Official Website: http://www.dunegames.com

Follow us on the official social media channels to stay up to date
Twitter: https://twitter.com/DuneSpiceWars
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/DuneSpiceWars/
